    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Completely Stretchy》是一款第一人称探索3D平台跳跃游戏，故事发生在奇异有趣的格隆比群岛上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 和格里布博士在电厂忙碌了一天之后，你发现自己变异了——身体变成蓝色，能够自由伸缩，而且超级黏！你不仅要忍受居民异样的眼光，更糟糕的是，电厂里的电灵逃跑了，在整个岛屿上横行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用你新获得的黏性力量进行攀爬，摆荡，黏连，探索这个奇妙的世界。找到隐藏的电灵，恢复工厂电力，解开你变身成超黏橡皮人的谜团——怎么就突然变成了一团蓝色的黏黏怪呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587570/extras/195b5205b2dc8a7256d4dc31ef084355.poster.avif?t=1770306302\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587570/extras/195b5205b2dc8a7256d4dc31ef084355.webm?t=1770306302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587570/extras/195b5205b2dc8a7256d4dc31ef084355.mp4?t=1770306302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 飞黏走壁：用你的手黏住一个点，然后在这个世界摇摆穿梭，找到隐藏的物品来帮助自己</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🖐️ 伸出黏手：帮助格隆比群岛上的古怪居民（比如斯克林布里和胖球），获得弹性升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ 再创新高：探索三个不同区域，每个区域的任务和活动都各有不同 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍄 着手快乐：跳上悬浮车，再扣几个篮，看看在这个疯狂的世界里你还能做些什么！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🤔 麻烦黏黏：与那些古怪的NPC们交谈，更加深入地了解这个世界<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587570/extras/265102e9be03201015a3e16cc394cc3b.poster.avif?t=1770306302\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587570/extras/265102e9be03201015a3e16cc394cc3b.webm?t=1770306302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587570/extras/265102e9be03201015a3e16cc394cc3b.mp4?t=1770306302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul>",
